        <qualifiedname>SYN_MotorOutput::set_output</qualifiedname>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Drive the motor at the given signed output level. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>The output range matches the controller&apos;s [output_min, output_max]. Positive = forward, negative = reverse, 0 = stop. The implementation must map this to the appropriate hardware command (PWM duty, step rate, etc.).</para>
