    <briefdescription>
<para>Abstract motor output interface (vtable). </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>The motor controller calls these functions to drive the motor without knowing the underlying hardware. This allows any motor driver to be used with syn_motor_ctrl, syn_autotune, etc. </para>
